      <h1>Overview</h1>
      <p>NASequencer is a text-based MIDI composition App.  It focuses on quick composing and easy management.  There have been several apps with musical notation for generating music sequence.  Generally, plain-text is easy to edit and manage, however it can often be unreadable in music composition.  NASequencer assists you to read structure of music composition by real-time previewing with piano roll and event list.  Additionally, it assists you to check sound of ensemble by SoundFont synthesizer.</p>
    </div>
